		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Second Sino-Japanese War</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<table class="infobox vevent" style="width: 315px; border-spacing: 2px; text-align: left; font-size: 90%;">
<tr>
<th class="summary" colspan="2" style="background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">Second Sino-Japanese War</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">Part of <a href="/wiki/World_War_II" title="World War II">World War II</a> and the <a href="/wiki/Pacific_War" title="Pacific War">Pacific War</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align: center; font-size: 90%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; line-height: 1.5em;"><a href="/wiki/File:Japanese_Occupation_-_Map.jpg" class="image" title="Japanese Occupation - Map.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fe/Japanese_Occupation_-_Map.jpg/300px-Japanese_Occupation_-_Map.jpg" width="300" height="229" border="0" /></a><br />
Map showing the extent of Japanese control in 1940.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2">
<table class="infobox" width="100%" style="margin: 0; cellpadding: 0; padding: 0; border: 0;">
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Date</th>
<td><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1937-07-07"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="07-07"><a href="/wiki/July_7" title="July 7">July 7</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1937" title="1937">1937</a></span> – <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1945-09-09"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="09-09"><a href="/wiki/September_9" title="September 9">September 9</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1945" title="1945">1945</a></span> (minor fighting since 1931)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Location</th>
<td><span class="location"><a href="/wiki/China" title="China">China</a></span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Result</th>
<td><a href="/wiki/Japanese_Instrument_of_Surrender" title="Japanese Instrument of Surrender">Unconditional surrender</a> of all Japanese forces in China to <a href="/wiki/Republic_of_China" title="Republic of China">ROC</a> with <a href="/wiki/Allies_of_World_War_II" title="Allies of World War II">Allied</a> victory in World War II.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right: 1em;">Territorial<br />
changes</th>
<td>Retrocession to <a href="/wiki/Republic_of_China" title="Republic of China">China</a> of <a href="/wiki/Manchuria" title="Manchuria">Manchuria</a>, and renunciation of sovereignty rights for <a href="/wiki/Taiwan" title="Taiwan">Taiwan</a> and <a href="/wiki/Penghu" title="Penghu">Penghu</a> according to the <a href="/wiki/San_Francisco_Peace_Treaty" title="San Francisco Peace Treaty" class="mw-redirect">San Francisco Peace Treaty</a></td>
</tr>
</table>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th colspan="2" style="background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">Belligerents</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="50%" style="border-right: 1px dotted #aaa;"><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Republic_of_China" title="Republic of China"><img alt="Flag of the Republic of China" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/72/Flag_of_the_Republic_of_China.svg/22px-Flag_of_the_Republic_of_China.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span><a href="/wiki/Republic_of_China" title="Republic of China">China</a><br />
<span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States"><img alt="Flag of the United States" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1a/US_flag_48_stars.svg/22px-US_flag_48_stars.svg.png" width="22" height="12" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States">United States</a><sup>1</sup><br />
<span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Soviet_Union" title="Soviet Union"><img alt="Flag of the Soviet Union" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/13/Flag_of_the_Soviet_Union_1923.svg/22px-Flag_of_the_Soviet_Union_1923.svg.png" width="22" height="11" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Soviet_Volunteer_Group" title="Soviet Volunteer Group">Soviet volunteers</a></td>
<td width="50%" style="padding-left: 0.25em;"><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Empire_of_Japan" title="Empire of Japan"><img alt="Flag of the Empire of Japan" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg/22px-Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Empire_of_Japan" title="Empire of Japan">Japan</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Collaborationist_Chinese_Army" title="Collaborationist Chinese Army">Collaborationist Chinese Army</a><sup>2</sup></td>
</tr>
