<td align="left" valign="top"><a name="Japan:__Imperial_Japanese_Army" id="Japan:__Imperial_Japanese_Army"></a>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Second_Sino-Japanese_War&amp;action=edit&amp;section=27" title="Edit section: Japan:  Imperial Japanese Army">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Japan: Imperial Japanese Army</span></h3>
<ul>
