<li><a href="/wiki/Toshizo_Nishio" title="Toshizo Nishio" class="mw-redirect">Toshizo Nishio</a> (<span lang="ja-Hant" xml:lang="ja-Hant">西尾 壽造</span>, <span lang="ja-Hani" xml:lang="ja-Hani">西尾 寿造</span>)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Yasuji_Okamura" title="Yasuji Okamura">Yasuji Okamura</a> (<span lang="ja-Hani" xml:lang="ja-Hani">岡村 寧次</span>)</li>
