<li><a href="/wiki/Prince_Takeda" title="Prince Takeda" class="mw-redirect">Prince Takeda</a> Tsuneyoshi (<span lang="ja-Hani" xml:lang="ja-Hani">竹田宮 恒徳王</span>)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Terauchi_Hisaichi" title="Terauchi Hisaichi" class="mw-redirect">Terauchi Hisaichi</a> (<span lang="ja-Hant" xml:lang="ja-Hant">寺内 壽一</span>, <span lang="ja-Hani" xml:lang="ja-Hani">寺内 寿一</span>)</li>
