<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Second_Sino-Japanese_War&amp;action=edit&amp;section=30" title="Edit section: Military engagements of the Second Sino-Japanese War">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Military engagements of the Second Sino-Japanese War</span></h2>
<p><a name="Battles" id="Battles"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Second_Sino-Japanese_War&amp;action=edit&amp;section=31" title="Edit section: Battles">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Battles</span></h3>
<p>Battles with articles. Flag shows victorious side in each engagement. Date shows beginning date except for the 1942 battle of Changsha, which began in Dec. 1941.</p>
<ul>
<li><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Japan" title="Japan"><img alt="Flag of Japan" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg/22px-Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Mukden_Incident" title="Mukden Incident">Mukden</a> September 1931</li>
<li><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Japan" title="Japan"><img alt="Flag of Japan" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg/22px-Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Invasion_of_Manchuria" title="Invasion of Manchuria">Invasion of Manchuria</a> September 1931
<ul>
<li><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Japan" title="Japan"><img alt="Flag of Japan" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg/22px-Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Jiangqiao_Campaign" title="Jiangqiao Campaign">Jiangqiao Campaign</a> October 1931</li>
<li><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Japan" title="Japan"><img alt="Flag of Japan" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg/22px-Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Resistance_at_Nenjiang_Bridge" title="Resistance at Nenjiang Bridge">Resistance at Nenjiang Bridge</a> November 1931</li>
<li><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Japan" title="Japan"><img alt="Flag of Japan" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg/22px-Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Chinchow_Operation" title="Chinchow Operation">Jinzhou</a> December 1931</li>
<li><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Japan" title="Japan"><img alt="Flag of Japan" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg/22px-Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Defense_of_Harbin" title="Defense of Harbin">Defense of Harbin</a> January 1932</li>
