</li>
<li><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Japan" title="Japan"><img alt="Flag of Japan" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg/22px-Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Japan" title="Japan"><img alt="Flag of Japan" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4f/Naval_Ensign_of_Japan.svg/22px-Naval_Ensign_of_Japan.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/January_28_Incident" title="January 28 Incident">Shanghai (1932)</a> January 1932</li>
<li><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Japan" title="Japan"><img alt="Flag of Japan" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg/22px-Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Pacification_of_Manchukuo" title="Pacification of Manchukuo">Pacification of Manchukuo</a> March 1932</li>
<li><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Japan" title="Japan"><img alt="Flag of Japan" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg/22px-Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Defense_of_the_Great_Wall" title="Defense of the Great Wall">Great Wall</a> January 1933
