<li><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Japan" title="Japan"><img alt="Flag of Japan" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e2/Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg/22px-Flag_of_Japan_-_variant.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Battle_of_Rehe" title="Battle of Rehe">Battle of Rehe</a> February 1933</li>
